  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.15.0-beta01\" data-text=\"Version 1.15.0-beta01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.15.0-beta01</h3>\n<p>October 2, 2024</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core:core:1.15.0-beta01</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core:core-ktx:1.15.0-beta01</code>, and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core:core-testing:1.15.0-beta01</code> are released. Version 1.15.0-beta01 contains <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/6b2638e1bfd54531dae1f04b33829101af8bf350..488540191ae5d26a91fb9d37f3c081c77f8dd4a7/core\">these commits</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">itemCount</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">importantForAccessibilityItemCount</code> fields to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">CollectionInfoCompat</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Ibaf349887f2c40ba63cd8b38033050953b96204b\">Ibaf34</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix documentation issues in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core.os.Profiling</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I2542f0d8c61c3475990e570b52810ee988b705da\">I2542f</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
